QTGZManager is a T?Z package  management  application that uses
standard  pkgtools  (present in any Slackware based system)  to
manage the  OS  software. It  provides  an  easy  to  use  four
pane view (directories, packages in the selected dir, installed
packages in the system  and package actions), drag and drop and
context menu support.

http://qtgzmanager.wordpress.com